Name: BeatNClean
About the game: Continue to save the subway from the garbage and the society from the garbage-loving people who pollute the environment by walking along the deserted roads of the subway with your sister You can take damage while attacking trash-loving people in your awesome moves. Don’t be afraid. You can keep fighting trash-loving people by collecting health bars along the way. The weight of the trash and the trash-loving people attacking you will reduce its stamina. Don’t forget! Reaching the highest score will bring you a cleaner society. If you want the winners to be eco-friendly people, never give up! Features: Infinite Gameplay Stylized Graphics
